konforka
------------------------------------------
konforka library is a convenience library which is supposed to soak in some
code common to our projects. It is not likely that you want to try this out
unless you need it as a dependency for other project. This is why you should
not expect a lengthier description here.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libkonforka-devel-0.0+git20070411-1bl4
  libkonforka0-0.0+git20070411-1bl4
  libpqxx-devel-4.0.1-1
  libpqxx4.0-4.0.1-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libpqxx-devel-4.0.1-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  libxslt-1.1.43-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/klevernothings/konforka

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/klevernothings/konforka.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack konforka-0.0+git20070411-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./konforka-0.0+git20070411-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/konforka-0.0+git20070411-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/konforka-0.0+git20070411-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkonforka0-0.0+git20070411-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkonforka-devel-0.0+git20070411-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(konforka)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/konforka.README
  /usr/share/doc/konforka/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/konforka/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/konforka/NEWS

(libkonforka0)
  /usr/bin/cygkonforka-0.dll

(libkonforka-devel)
  /usr/include/konforka/basic_wrapper.h
  /usr/include/konforka/exception.h
  /usr/include/konforka/pointer_map.h
  /usr/include/konforka/pqxx_pile.h
  /usr/include/konforka/resource_pile.h
  /usr/include/konforka/responsible_wrapper.h
  /usr/include/konforka/util.h
  /usr/lib/libkonforka.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/konforka.pc

